claim.claim-text:
5. A substrate processing apparatus comprising:
a depressurizable processing chamber;
a mounting electrode installed within the processing chamber and configured to mount a processing target substrate;
a facing electrode installed so as to face the mounting electrode; and
a gas flow path structure, as claimed in claim 1, that supplies a processing gas between the mounting electrode and the facing electrode,
wherein plasma is excited from the processing gas supplied between the mounting electrode and the facing electrode, and a plasma process is performed on the processing target substrate by the plasma.
